§7§oConstantly consumes LP to speed up plant growth.

If there is will in the chunk, the ritual can be upgraded:

Raw: increased speed

Corrosive: entities are damaged for extra plant speed

Destructive: the more will, the faster

Vengeful: increases frequency of growth ticks

Steadfast: replants crops, and hydrates soil with no water
